snippet.title: Tere Bin Ep 03 - [Eng Sub] - Digitally Presented by Nisa Cosmetics - Yumna Zaidi - Wahaj Ali
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Tere Bin Episode 03 - [Eng Sub] - Yumna Zaidi - Wahaj Ali - Digitally Presented by Nisa Hair Removal Cream - 4th January 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Tere Bin Digitally presented by Nisa Cosmetics

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab’s life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family’s decision regarding her and Murtasim’s life. Meerab’s hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab’s arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim’s family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Writer: Nooran Makhdoom
Director: Siraj ul Haq
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

Cast :
Yumna Zaidi as Meerab
Wahaj Ali as Murtasim
Bushra Ansari as Salma
Sohail Sameer as Anwar
Sabeena Farooq as Haya
Hira Soomro as Maryam
Fazila Qazi as Aneela
Farhan Ally Agha as Waqas
Seemi Pasha as Sabra
Mahmood Aslam as Malik Mukhtaar
Haris Waheed
Agha Mustafa

snippet.title: Hostel Hudugaru Protest Song | Hostel Hudugaru Bekagiddare | Ajaneesh Loknath |Nithin Krishnamurthy
snippet.description:
Kantara music director B. Ajaneesh Loknath comes with another magical creation in Nithin Krishnamurthy's directorial debut, Hostel Hudugaru Bekagiddare. The first single "Hostel Hudugaru Protest Song" sung by the Music director himself and penned by Yogarajbhat Fans is an another attraction for the film. Hostel Hudugaru Bekagiddare is a one-of-a-kind found-footage comedy-drama that is set entirely inside a boy's hostel, featuring 500 new talents and cameo by superstars, Rishab Shetty, Ramya, Pavan Kumar & Shine Shetty.  The film is made under the Gulmohar films banner in association with Varrun Studios. The director who has also served as one of the four producers of the film along with Prajwal B.P., Varun Kumar, and Arvind S. Kashyap, who is handling cinematography as well and Presented by Paramvah Pictures.

Listen to the song on all your favorite Music platforms : https://bfan.link/hostel-hudugaru-protest-song

https://bit.ly/SubscribeToA2Music for more !

#HostelHudugaruProtestSong #a2music #HostelHudugaruBekagiddare #kannadamovies #kannadasongs

snippet.title: Tere Bin Episode 05 Teaser - 5th January 2023 - HAR PAL GEO
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Tere Bin Episode 05 Teaser - 5th January 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab’s life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family’s decision regarding her and Murtasim’s life. Meerab’s hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab’s arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim’s family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Writer: Nooran Makhdoom
Director: Siraj ul Haq
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

snippet.title: തിരുവാതിര പുണ്യം നേടിത്തരുന്ന ശിവപാർവ്വതിമാരുടെ ഭക്തിസാന്ദ്രമായ ഗാനങ്ങൾ | Thiruvathira Special Songs
snippet.description:
തിരുവാതിര പുണ്യം നേടിത്തരുന്ന ശിവപാർവ്വതിമാരുടെ ഭക്തിസാന്ദ്രമായ ഗാനങ്ങൾ | Thiruvathira Special Songs
Thiruvathira is a Hindu festival which is celebrated on Thiruvathira Nakshatra in the malayalam Month of Dhanu.Thiruvathira is the night of Makairam Nakshatra and Thiruvathira, the birthday of Lord Shiva.Thiruvairanikulam Mahadeva Temple is the most famous temple during the Dhanumasa Thiruvathira festival. Thiruvairanikulam Mahadeva Temple is also known as the Sabarimala of women, enshrining Lord Shiva and Parvati. Although the deities of Lord Shiva and Parvati are in the same shrine, both of them face different directions. Shiva faces east and Parvati faces west.The Nata of Goddess Parvathi in Thiruvairanikulam temple is opened in Thiruvathira in the month of Dhanu.Thiruvathirakali or Kaikottikali is a unique dance performed in Kerala on the auspicious day of Thiruvathira, the birthday of Lord Shiva.As per Hindu mythology, this dance is what brought Kamadeva (God of Love) back to life when he had been burnt to ashes by Lord Shiva's fury.According to Hindu belief that,Lord Shiva agreed to marry Goddess Parvati as a result of severe penance on Thiruvathira. It is believed that observing Dhanumasa Tiruvathira vratam according to fate will bring prosperity, long sumangaliyoga and happy married life.

localized.title: തിരുവാതിര പുണ്യം നേടിത്തരുന്ന ശിവപാർവ്വതിമാരുടെ ഭക്തിസാന്ദ്രമായ ഗാനങ്ങൾ | Thiruvathira Special Songs
localized.description:
തിരുവാതിര പുണ്യം നേടിത്തരുന്ന ശിവപാർവ്വതിമാരുടെ ഭക്തിസാന്ദ്രമായ ഗാനങ്ങൾ | Thiruvathira Special Songs
Thiruvathira is a Hindu festival which is celebrated on Thiruvathira Nakshatra in the malayalam Month of Dhanu.Thiruvathira is the night of Makairam Nakshatra and Thiruvathira, the birthday of Lord Shiva.Thiruvairanikulam Mahadeva Temple is the most famous temple during the Dhanumasa Thiruvathira festival. Thiruvairanikulam Mahadeva Temple is also known as the Sabarimala of women, enshrining Lord Shiva and Parvati. Although the deities of Lord Shiva and Parvati are in the same shrine, both of them face different directions. Shiva faces east and Parvati faces west.The Nata of Goddess Parvathi in Thiruvairanikulam temple is opened in Thiruvathira in the month of Dhanu.Thiruvathirakali or Kaikottikali is a unique dance performed in Kerala on the auspicious day of Thiruvathira, the birthday of Lord Shiva.As per Hindu mythology, this dance is what brought Kamadeva (God of Love) back to life when he had been burnt to ashes by Lord Shiva's fury.According to Hindu belief that,Lord Shiva agreed to marry Goddess Parvati as a result of severe penance on Thiruvathira. It is believed that observing Dhanumasa Tiruvathira vratam according to fate will bring prosperity, long sumangaliyoga and happy married life.

snippet.title: വാതം മാറാനുള്ള ഭക്ഷണങ്ങൾ | സന്ധിവേദന, സന്ധിവാതം ആമവാതം എന്നിവ  മാറ്റിയെടുക്കാം | @Arogyam
snippet.description:
വാതം മാറാനുള്ള ഭക്ഷണങ്ങൾ | സന്ധിവേദന, സന്ധിവാതം ആമവാതം എന്നിവ  മാറ്റിയെടുക്കാം. Effective diet for arthritis, arthritis diet malayalam

വാതം മാറ്റിയെടുക്കാൻ ഈ ഭക്ഷണങ്ങൾ  ശ്രദ്ധിച്ചാൽ മതി
സന്ധിവേദന, സന്ധിവാതം ആമവാതം എന്നിവ ഇനി വരുതിയിലാക്കാം
വേദന സംഹാരികൾ തിന്നുതീർക്കുന്നവർ നിർബന്ധമായും കാണേണ്ട വീഡിയോ

ഇന്ന് വിവിധ തരം വേദനകൾ കൊണ്ട് കഷ്ടപ്പെടുന്നവർ നമുക്കിടയിൽ ധാരാളമുണ്ട്. അതിൽ തന്നെ വാദസംബന്ധമായ പ്രശ്നങ്ങൾ അലട്ടുന്നവരാണ് കൂടുതൽ. സന്ധിവാതം, തേയ്മാനം, റുമാറ്റോയിഡ് ആർത്രൈറ്റിസ് അഥവാ ആമവാതം യൂറിക് ആസിഡ് കൊണ്ടുള്ള വാത പ്രശ്നങ്ങൾ എന്നിവ ഇതിൽ പ്രധാനപ്പെട്ടതാണ്. 

വ്യായാമവും ഭക്ഷണവും ഒരുവിധം രോഗങ്ങൾക്ക് പരിഹാരമാണ് എന്ന് നമുക്കറിയാമല്ലോ. ഇത്തരത്തിൽ സന്ധിവാതം, ആമവാതം അഥവാ റൂമറ്റോയിഡ് ആർത്രൈറ്റിസ്, മറ്റുവാതങ്ങൾ, വിവിധതരം വേദനകൾ എന്നിവ നിയന്ത്രിക്കുന്നതിന് ഫലപ്രദമായ ഭക്ഷണരീതി  നിർദ്ദേശിക്കുകയാണ് പാണ്ടിക്കാട് ഡോക്ടർ ബാസിൽ ഹോമിയോ ആശുപത്രിയിലെ ഡോക്ടർ സെമിയ.

snippet.title: Bakra Nahi Majnu Halaal - Part 1 : Ek Se Bhali Do - Amit Bhadana
snippet.description:
Download Duolingo and learn any language for free - https://app.adjust.net.in/jgl36j4

Ye life achche achchon ko halaal kar deti hain lekin hamare Rinku ki kahani thodi different hain. Isne khud ja ke musibat se panga liya. Rinku ki life mast chal rahi thi. Bade sheher mein sarkari naukari ki tayyari kar raha tha aur ek girlfriend bhi thi, Raveena, jo isse apna naukar samajhti thi Par phir bhi Rinku apne roommate Neetu ke sath khush tha. Phir iski life mein aayi Sangeeta aur life mein 5th gear lag gaya. Ek ke baad ek kamaal hone laga aur apna Rinku halaal hone laga. Yakeen na ho to khud dekh lo. Ek aisi kahani jis mein music hai, drama hai, action hai ( Rinku ki life mein ) , romance hai aur bahut saari confusion ke sath double dose of comedy bhi hai. Full family ke sath enjoy this special presentation

snippet.title: HIGHLIGHTS | MAHREZ STRIKE SECURES CRUCIAL THREE POINTS AT CHELSEA | Chelsea 0-1 Man City
snippet.description:
Riyad Mahrez scored a second-half winner as City secured a 1-0 victory over Chelsea at Stamford Bridge to close the gap at the top of the Barclays Premier League.
The winger was in the perfect place to turn in Jack Grealish’s low cross in the 63rd minute to secure a big three points in a thrilling clash.
Chelsea’s Carney Chukwuemeka and Nathan Ake both hit the woodwork as City took the win to move within five points of leaders Arsenal.

Chelsea’s Carney Chukwuemeka and Nathan Ake both hit the woodwork as City took the win to move within five points of leaders Arsenal.

Tere Bin Episode 04 - [Eng Sub] - Yumna Zaidi - Wahaj Ali - Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream - 5th January 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Tere Bin Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab’s life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family’s decision regarding her and Murtasim’s life. Meerab’s hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab’s arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim’s family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

snippet.title: मैंने जबसे इस तरीके से पाव भाजी है बनाया तबसे सरे पुराने तरीको को बेकार पाया | Instant Pav Bhaji
snippet.description:
#pavbhaji #mumbaistyle #bhaji 

INGREIDENTS TO MAKE THE RECIPE:

2 Onions (Slices)
3 Desi Tomatoes 
1 Capsicum
1 Whole Garlic 
2 Inch Ginger 
2 - 3 Tbsp Butter 
Oil As Needed 
1 tsp Cumin Seeds 
1/2 tsp Turmeric Powder 
1 tsp Kashmiri Red Chilli Powder 
1 Tbsp Salt 
1/2 Beatroot 
1 - 2 Carrot 
1 Cup Peas
3 Potatoes 
250 - 300 Gms Cauli Flower 
1.5 Cups Water 
4 Tbsp Butter 
1 tsp Bleck Pepper Powder 
2 Tbsp Kasuri Methi 
 Coriander Leaves 

FOR TADKA 

3 - 4 Garlic Cloves (chopped )
1 Onion (Finely Chopped )
2 Tbsp Pav Bhaji Masala 

FOR PAV 

2 Tbsp Butter 
1 tsp Poav Bhaji Masala 
1/2 tsp Kashmiri Red Chilli Powder 
Coriander Leaves.

snippet.description:
Are you looking for a delicious and easy recipe to make Perfect Bellam Pakundalu? Look no further! In this video, I'll show you how to make this delicious and unique dish using simple ingredients that you likely have on hand.

#VismaiFood #VismaiFoodRecipies

This pakundalu recipe is a sankranthi special recipe in the coastal region of Andhra Pradesh, especially the Godavari districts and uttharandhras. It's a unique and delicious dish that everyone will love. If you're looking for a dish that will show off your cooking skills, this is the recipe for you!

For detailed recipes with Ingredients and Methods in English & Telugu visit https://www.vismaifood.com/

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3660 - 5 Jan 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3660: Bagha's Date 
--------------------------------------------------------
Nattu Kaka shares some exciting news about the business deals of Gada Electronics, which makes Jethalal very happy. Jethalal gets impressed with his employees' performances and gifts them brand-new phones. Bagha notices Jethalal's happy mood and decides to ask for the day off to go on a date with Bawri. Jetha grants Bagha a day off, and he is off to meet Bawri. Is Bawri excited about Bagha as well? She has some news to share with Bagha; what does she have to say to him? 

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Raj Anankat
Episodes No - 3660, 5 Jan 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab 

Click here to subscribe to SAB TV:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Click here to subscribe to SonyLIV: 
http://www.sonyliv.com/signin

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. Jethalal lives in Gokuldham society and owns an electronics shop.  'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

Click here to watch the episode of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah :
https://www.sonyliv.com/dplnk?schema=sony://asset/1000203269

snippet.title: Paneer Butter Masala | होटल जैसा पनीर बटर मसाला | Restaurant Style | Chef Sanjyot Keer
snippet.description:
Full  written recipe for Paneer Butter Masala

Prep time: 10-15 minutes
Cooking time: 20-25 minutes
Serves: 4-5 people

Ingredients:
Paste
TOMATO | टमाटर 4 NOS. 
GARLIC | लेहसुन 8-10 CLOVES. 
GINGER | अदरक 1 INCH
CORIANDER STEMS | धनिया के डंठल 2 TBSP
GREEN CHILLI | हरी मिर्च 1 NO. 
KASHMIRI / DEGI RED CHILLI POWDER | कश्मीरी / देगी लाल मिर्च पाउडर 1.5 TBSP
CORIANDER POWDER | धनिया पाउडर 1 TBSP
CUMIN POWDER | जीरा पाउडर 1/2 TSP
CASHEW | काजू 15 NOS. (SOAKED)
Paneer sauteing
OIL | तेल 1 TBSP
BUTTER | मक्खन 1 TBSP
PANEER | पनीर 500 GRAMS (CUBED)
SALT | नमक TO TASTE
KASHMIRI RED CHILLI POWDER | कश्मीरी लाल मिर्च पाउडर A PINCH
Final Cooking:
OIL | तेल 2 TBSP
BUTTER | मक्खन 1 TBSP
WHOLE SPICES
CUMIN SEEDS | जीरा 1 TSP
GREEN CARDAMOM | हरी इलायची 3 NOS. 
CINNAMON | दालचीनी 1/2 INCH
BAY LEAF | तेज पत्ता 1 NO. 
GARLIC | लेहसुन 1 TBSP (CHOPPED)
GREEN CHILLI | हरी मिर्च 1 NO. (CHOPPED)
ONION | प्याज़ 3 MEDIUM SIZED (CHOPPED)
TURMERIC POWDER | हल्दी पाउडर 1/4 TSP
KASHMIRI RED CHILLI POWDER | कश्मीरी लाल मिर्च पाउडर 1/2 TSP
SALT | नमक TO TASTE
SUGAR | शक्कर A PINCH 
HOT WATER | गरम पानी AS REQUIRED
BUTTER | मक्खन 2 TBSP
ROASTED KASURI METHI POWDER | भुनी हुई कसूरी मेथी पाउडर A PINCH
GARAM MASALA | गरम मसाला A PINCH
FRESH CREAM | फ्रेश क्रीम 3-4 TBSP
FRESH CORIANDER | हरा धनिया AS REQUIRED (CHOPPED)
Method:
Add all the ingredients of the paste into a mixer grinder jar & grind it into a fine paste, make sure you soak the cashews in boiling water for 10-15 minutes before adding it, you can also boil it for 5 minutes.
To sauté the paneer, set a pan over high heat & once it gets hot, add the oil & butter.
Once the oil gets hot, add the cubed paneer, salt & kashmiri red chilli powder, then toss the paneer over high flame for 1-2 minutes, doing this step will help the paneer to hold its structure in the gravy, once sauteed remove the paneer into a bowl & set it aside until you make the gravy.
To make the gravy, heat a wok or a kadhai then add oil & butter, once the oil gets hot, add all the whole spices along with, garlic & chopped green chilli, stir well & then add the onions & cook over medium high flame until the onions turn light golden brown.
Once the onions turn light golden brown add turmeric powder & kashmiri red chilli powder, stir well & then add a splash of hot water, stir well & cook the masala for 2-3 minutes.
Further add the prepared paste along with salt & sugar, stir well & cook over medium high flame until the oil separates.
Once the oil separates add hot water as required to adjust the gravy then cook for 2-3 minutes, then taste the gravy & adjust the seasoning accordingly.
Further add the paneer, butter & all the remaining ingredients, stir well & cook only for 1-2 minutes & then finally sprinkle some more fresh coriander.
Your paneer butter masala is ready, serve hot with naan, tandoori roti or rumali roti.

#YFL #SanjyotKeer #paneerbuttermasala

snippet.title: Every Indian Wedding Ever | Ft. Tena Jaiin | The Paayal Jain
snippet.description:
Hey Guys
This Video shows all the crazy fun that happens in Big Fat Indian weddings. Relatives giving advices about marriage. All the money , gifts , wedding preps , indian food , gol gappe , tikki , chart items , Paneer Tikka ,  spicy food , indian sweets , shaadi lehenga , bride makeup , wedding shopping , crazy dancing on wedding songs . Indian aunties taking lime light . Mehendi functions getting henna done and celebrating with family , friends , cousins . बऱ्याच वेळा स्वयंपाक घरात काम करत असताना काही गोष्टी खूप सोप्या असतात पण माहीत नसल्याने आपण करत नाही किंवा अवघड पद्धतीने करतो. काही नवशिके, नव्याने स्वयंपाक शिकणारी मुले, नवीन लग्न झालेल्या मुली यांना या गोष्टी अवघड जातात. नव्याने स्वयंपाक शिकणाऱ्यांसाठी किचन टिप्स, किचन टिप्स, किचन उपयुक्त महत्वाच्या किचन टिप्स. यावर आधीच विडियो बनवले आहेत, पण आज आपण स्वयंपाक करत असताना भाज्या कशा चिराव्यात ही पाहणार आहोत. कांदा बारीक कसं कापावा कोबी कसा कापावा? व्हेज कटलेट साथी भजया कश्या कापाव्यात? ही समजत नाहीत. इथे मी सोप्या पद्धती सांगितल्या आहेत. तुमचे स्वयंपाकतील कामे सोपी होतील. स्वयंपाक करताना उशीर होतो? पसारा होतो? मग हा विडियो शेवटपर्यंत नक्की पहा. सुगरण होण्यासाठी या गोष्टी माहिती असायलाच हव्यात. 
सुगरण होण्यासाठी या 10 गोष्टी माहिती असायलाच हव्यात. या महत्वपूर्ण 10 किचन टिप्स मी संगत आहे. तुम्हाला नक्कीच उपयुक्त येतील.

खमंग तीळाची पोळी। या 7 टिप्स वापरून बनवा 8 दिवस टिकणारी कडेपर्यंत सारण पसरून खुसखुशीत तीळ गूळ पोळी  https://youtu.be/E6xtq4FoXuI

snippet.title: Recipe 669: Thiruvadhirai Kali & Thazhaga Kuzhambu
snippet.description:
#Ingredients

#Thiruvadhirai_Kali

Raw Rice - 1 cup
Moong Dal - 1 spoon
Jaggery - 2 cup
Water - 3 cup
Cardamom Powder - 1/2 tsp
Coconut - 1/4 (Grated)
Ghee - 1 tbsp
Cashew Nuts

#Thazhaga_Kuzhambu

Black Sesame - 2 tsp
Raw Rice - 2 tsp
Oil - 1 tsp
Gram Dal - 2 tsp
Urad Dal - 1 tsp
Fenugreek - 1/4 tsp
Dry Chilli - 10 nos
Grated Coconut - 4 spoon
Curry Leaves
Taro Root - 1/4 kg
Yam - 1/4 kg
Raw - 1/4 kg
Banana - 1/4 kg
Sweet Potato - 1/4 kg
Carrot - 1/4 kg
Broad Beans - 1/4 kg
Yellow Pumpkin - 1/4 kg
Ash Gourd - 1/4 kg
Water as required
Salt to taste
Asafoetida - 1/2 tsp
Jaggery (optional)
Tamarind Water - 2 cup
Coconut oil - 1 tbsp
Mustard - 1 spoon
Grated Coconut - 4 spoon
Curry Leaves

snippet.title: Evil Dead Rise – Official Trailer (Red Band)
snippet.description:
New Line Cinema and Renaissance Pictures present a return to the iconic horror franchise, “Evil Dead Rise,” from writer/director Lee Cronin (“The Hole in the Ground”). The movie stars Lily Sullivan (“I Met a Girl,” “Barkskins”), Alyssa Sutherland (“The Mist,” “Vikings”), Morgan Davies (“Storm Boy,” “The End”), Gabrielle Echols (“Reminiscence”) and introducing Nell Fisher (“Northspur”). 

Website: www.warnerbros-india.com
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/WarnerBrosIndia
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/warnerbrosindia
Twitter: https://twitter.com/warnerbrosindia

Moving the action out of the woods and into the city, “Evil Dead Rise” tells a twisted tale of two estranged sisters, played by Sutherland and Sullivan, whose reunion is cut short by the rise of flesh-possessing demons, thrusting them into a primal battle for survival as they face the most nightmarish version of family imaginable.
“Evil Dead Rise” is produced by Rob Tapert (“Ash vs Evil Dead,” “Don’t Breathe”) and executive produced by series creator and horror icon Sam Raimi and cult legend and “Ash” himself, Bruce Campbell, along with John Keville, Macdara Kelleher, Richard Brener, Dave Neustadter, Romel Adam and Victoria Palmieri.
Cronin is joined behind the camera by director of photography Dave Garbett (“Z for Zachariah,” “Underworld: Rise of the Lycans”), production designer Nick Bassett (“Guns Akimbo,” “Sweet Tooth”), editor Bryan Shaw (“Ash vs Evil Dead,” “Spartacus”) and costume designer Sarah Voon (“Chasing Great,” “Inside”), with a score by Stephen McKeon (“The Hole in the Ground,” “Primeval”).
A New Line Cinema / Renaissance Pictures presentation of a Pacific Renaissance and Wild Atlantic Pictures production, “Evil Dead Rise” will be distributed worldwide by Warner Bros. Pictures and is set to open in cinemas in India on April 21, 2023.

#WarnerBrosIndia #EvilDeadRise #EvilDeadRiseTrailer

snippet.title: Bihaan के साथ हुआ हादसा | Thapki Pyar Ki | थपकी प्यार की | Full Episode | Ep. 582
snippet.description:
To download the Voot app please click on the link: https://voot.onelink.me/eIb4/9b2f5423

To subscribe to this channel, go to: https://www.youtube.com/c/ColorsRishtey1/featured

Watching Thapki leave, Bihaan follows her on the bike and meets with an accident. Is Shraddha responsible for this? Seven years pass by, Sankar and Shraddha now rule the Pandey house and ill-treat Thapki's daughter, Tina. Will Thapki and Bihaan ever return to the Pandey household? 

The bright and beautiful Thapki is pretty much perfect... except for one minor flaw - she stammers. But that doesn't hold her back. All she needs is an encouraging pat on the back,a 'thapki', which soon becomes her name. Over the course of the show, Thapki falls in love with Dhruv, but is duped into getting married to his brother, Bihaan. In spite of this cruel twist of fate, Thapki doesn't let her spirit fade and does all she can to be the ideal bahu. What does destiny hold for this charming girl with an unbeatable spirit?

snippet.title: Lakadbaggha - Official Trailer | Anshuman Jha, Ridhi Dogra, Milind Soman & Paresh Pahuja | 13th Jan
snippet.description:
Music 👉🏻 SUBSCRIBE to Zee Music Company - https://bit.ly/2yPcBkS 

Animal Lover Vigilante vs Animal Abuser Kingpin.

Present Day - “Street dogs across Kolkata are disappearing” - An antagonist runs a crazy wicked agency using the Kolkata port to sell animals - from rare turtles to (extinct) birds - but on the side also takes up illegal contracts from middle class bengali "bhodroloks" (Gen-tlemen) to take out "disturbing" street dogs.

A protagonist, who lets his punches and flying kicks (Krav-Maga) do all the talking and becomes the much needed voice of our turmoiled co-habitants (Dogs) on the planet. But it ain’t just an action movie.

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3659 - 4 Jan 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3659: Bagha Has Good News For Jetha
--------------------------------------------------------
Jetha tries to explain the significance of Bhide's written thoughts on the bulletin board of society. The children are perplexed by his explanations, so Iyer steps in and explains the true meaning. He also talks about the importance of the Sanskrit language. Iyer discusses the Rishis who mentioned "Brahmastra," the most powerful weapon, in Sanskrit scriptures. Later, Bagha rushes into the shop, claiming to have some exciting news for his boss, Jetha. Watch the episode to learn more!

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Raj Anankat
Episodes No - 3659, 4 Jan 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab 

Click here to subscribe to SAB TV:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Click here to subscribe to SonyLIV: 
http://www.sonyliv.com/signin

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. Jethalal lives in Gokuldham society and owns an electronics shop.  'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

Click here to watch the episode of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah :
https://www.sonyliv.com/dplnk?schema=sony://asset/1000203086

Radhakrishn Raasleela- part 243 | Krishn Ne kiya Rukmini Se Prashn | Radhakrishn | राधाकृष्ण
Radhakrishn Raasleela- part 243 | Krishn Ne kiya Rukmini Se Prashn | Radhakrishn | राधाकृष्ण


►*About*
-------------
RadhaKrishn ke shaashwat prem ke vishay mein to sabhi ko gyaat hai. Radha bina Krishn nahin aur Krishn bina nahin Radha! Yadi Krishn Hriday hain, to Radha us hriday ki gati. Is premi yugal ki is mahagaatha mein aap jaanenge ki kis tarah Radha aur Krishn ne apne prem ko sansaar mein sthaapit kiya aur samast sansaar ko prem ki paribhasha sikhaayi, kyonki prem to bahut se log karte hain kintu keval prem ko paane ke liye… parantu RadhaKrishn ka prem ek-doosre ko paane ke liye nahin, apitu sansaar ko prem sikhaane ke liye tha. To dekhte rahiye RadhaKrishn ki ye anokhi prem-gaatha, jo Krishn nahin, apitu Radha ki drishti se likhee gayi hai!


Jaanne ke liye dekhiye #RadhaKrishn, Somvaar se Shanivaar, shaam 7.30 baje, sirf #StarBharat par. Krishn aur Radha ki leelaon se judde rehne ke liye hamein follow kariye Instagram, Facebook aur YouTube par!

#radhakrishn #starbharat #dildekedekhozara #mythology #राधाकृष्ण
#radhakrishna #sumallika #mallikasingh #radha

snippet.description:
Jethalal arranged for a pastry party for the kids. All the people enjoyed the pastries with tasty food. Bapuji and Jetha got involved in an emotional moment with each other. Suddenly Goli stopped them, to know more watch the full episode.

Show Name - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast - Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt
Episode -  3492
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi, Neela Asit Modi

#taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #livcomedy #tmkoc #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा 

Click here to Subscribe to LIV Comedy: 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCBIT1FSJW6yTlzqK-31FDWg?sub_confirmation=1

About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal’s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in 'Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

Click here to watch all the comedy clips of your favorite show:
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLSXTaG1fT0cROTR5KlBGLJy5K8Rhpwt2W

snippet.title: क्या फिर से मिलेंगे Thapki और Bihaan? | Thapki Pyar Ki | थपकी प्यार की | Full Episode | Ep. 583
snippet.description:
To download the Voot app please click on the link: https://voot.onelink.me/eIb4/9b2f5423

To subscribe to this channel, go to: https://www.youtube.com/c/ColorsRishtey1/featured

After walking out of Bihaan's life, Thapki now lives with her daughter Bani. While Bani's life is full of happiness, Tina faces harassment at the hands of Shraddha and Sankar at the Pandey house. Will Thapki and Bihaan cross paths?

The bright and beautiful Thapki is pretty much perfect... except for one minor flaw - she stammers. But that doesn't hold her back. All she needs is an encouraging pat on the back,a 'thapki', which soon becomes her name. Over the course of the show, Thapki falls in love with Dhruv, but is duped into getting married to his brother, Bihaan. In spite of this cruel twist of fate, Thapki doesn't let her spirit fade and does all she can to be the ideal bahu. What does destiny hold for this charming girl with an unbeatable spirit?

snippet.title: Marrying A Village Girl Ft. Abhinav Anand & Bhavya Sharma | Webseries | Hasley India
snippet.description:
“Jab pyaar kiya toh darna kya” holds true for every situation that happens when people are in love, be it anything.

Download the inDrive app - https://share.indrive.com/lhG6/sidebyside

Being intimate with someone even if they are your partner has always been a topic that brings awkwardness between people.

And when this happens to a couple who just had an arranged marriage, it becomes worse, kyunki na jaan na pehchaan hum tere mehnaan!

Here with this episode of Side by Side, Hasley India brings to you a story of one such couple who face intimacy issues just because of the fact that they don’t know each other. And when there are these issues, it becomes harder to cope with things.

But instead of every obstacle in their way, how they decide to be with each other, Side by Side; is what makes their bond stronger and special.

Let’s experience this bumpy ride together! Watch the episode till the end.
